Why mockup desing tools we will use?
------------------------------------
After software requirement analysis, we need to create demo design of each pages to show client to confirmation before
start coding. Figma is a mockup tool (there are some other mockup tools of different company) use to create demo design.

www.figma.com
-------------------

FilePlace Image 	:  	ctrl + shift + k
FileSave local copy
EditUndo		: 	ctrl+Z
EditRedo		: 	ctrl+Y
EditFind		: 	Ctrl+F
EditPick Color	:	 I
EditSelect All		: 	Ctrl+A
ViewPixel Grid	: 	Shift+’
ViewLayout Grid 	: 	Shift + G
ViewRulers 		: 	Shift + R
ViewComments 	: 	Shift + C
ViewShow/Hide UI	: 	Ctrl+\
ViewZoom in		:	Ctrl++
ViewZoom out	:	Ctrl+-
ViewZoom to 100%	:	Ctrl+0
ObjectGroup Selection: 	Ctrl+G
ObjectBring Forward	:	Ctrl+]
ObjectSend Backward:	Ctrl+[
ObjectSend Back	:	[
Copy object and Paste     : press mouse right button + Alt and move some where              
Move			:	V
Scale/Ratio		:	K     
Ractangle box		:	R
Line			:	L


Layout grid:
-------------------
type: column 
	count:12     //number of column
	color:FF000
	type: Strech
	Width: auto
	Margin: 135   //left and right
	Gutter: 20    //distance between column


  
